result.name: Northern Dumpling Yuan

reviews.text: Serviceable dumpling place with low prices and lots of options. They are a bit bland, but since service is fast and the prices are low, Northern Yuan has its place as a lunch or guilty pleasure takeout joint. It has a certain amount of deserved neighborhood institution status too. Northern Yuan won’t be the best dumpling you’ve ever had, but it’s tasty and priced right.
LOVE this place. Really good dumplings, quick, and reasonable prices. Been back several times and it’s always good. Can be crowded at times.
Good for foreigner to try northern China style dumplings. However, the taste is not the same as what we tried in around 2007.

Small Northern Dumpling Restauramt with great varieties quality dumplings and appetizer. Although the restaurant is very small, many locals and tourists do visit this restaurant so often. Many different ingredients of dumplings which I never seen in other restaurants like that. It is great for dumping lovers. All types of quality and juicy dumplings are priced reasonably.  You will definitely like it.
One of my favourite places in HK. Because it was around the corner from our apartment, we went often and took guest when they visited. We all loved it!
